    "Vzdálené ovládání z prohlížeče v LAN — HTTPS + Basic Auth. Self-signed certifikát, prohlížeč jednorázově varuje (Advanced → Pokračovat).": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Remote control from a browser on the LAN — HTTPS + Basic Auth. Self-signed certificate; the browser warns once (Advanced → Continue)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "PŘIHLÁŠENÍ (uživatel / heslo)": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "LOGIN (user / password)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pravidla: min. 12 znaků; alespoň 3 typy znaků (velká písmena, malá, číslice, speciální); žádný známý vzor jako \"admin\", \"heslo\", \"12345\", \"qwerty\".": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Rules: min. 12 chars; at least 3 character types (uppercase, lowercase, digits, symbols); no common patterns like \"admin\", \"password\", \"12345\", \"qwerty\"."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Heslo splňuje pravidla": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Password meets the rules"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "IP WHITELIST (volitelné)": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "IP WHITELIST (optional)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "CIDR ranges oddělené čárkou. Když prázdné, povolené všechny IP. Např.: 192.168.0.0/24, 10.0.0.0/8": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "CIDR ranges separated by commas. Empty = all IPs allowed. Example: 192.168.0.0/24, 10.0.0.0/8"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Načítám…": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Loading…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "macOS vybírá rozhraní podle routovací tabulky (nejbližší subnet + metric). V kartě Kamery vidíš u každé IP info Route přes: enX — tak poznáš, zda stream jde přes ethernet (en0) nebo WiFi (en1).": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "macOS picks the interface based on the routing table (closest subnet + metric). On the Cameras card you'll see Route via: enX next to each IP — that tells you whether the stream goes over Ethernet (en0) or Wi-Fi (en1)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Znovu vygenerovat certifikát": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Regenerate certificate"
          }
