          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The app reads how many frames per second the camera sends (e.g. 10) and uses that value. Recommended to leave on — disable only if you want to reduce CPU load."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Ručně snímků za vteřinu": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Manual frames per second"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Stejná frekvence jako zachycení (viz výše). Odškrtni pokud chceš čtení SPZ provádět méně často než příjem snímků — šetří to CPU.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Same rate as capture (see above). Disable if you want plate reading to run less often than frame capture — saves CPU."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Úsporný režim": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Idle mode"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Když není po nastavenou dobu detekována žádná SPZ, aplikace sníží frekvenci OCR čtení na nastavenou idle hodnotu. Tím se šetří CPU/ANE/energie. Jakmile Vision detekuje motion nebo plate, okamžitě naběhne zpět na plnou rychlost.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When no plate is detected for the set duration, the app lowers the OCR rate to the idle value. This saves CPU/ANE/energy. As soon as Vision sees motion or a plate, full rate resumes immediately."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Přepnout po": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Switch after"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Po jaké době neaktivity (sekundy bez Vision detekce) přepnout do úsporného režimu. 2 s je rozumné — kratší znamená časté přepínání, delší znamená menší úsporu.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "After how long without activity (seconds without Vision detection) to switch to idle. 2 s is reasonable — shorter means frequent switching, longer means less savings."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Cílové fps v úspoře": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Target fps when idle"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "OCR fps během úsporného režimu. 1 fps = 1 OCR cyklus za vteřinu, výrazná úspora. Vyšší hodnota (2–5) sníží reakční čas na auto vjíždějící do scény bez motion detekce. 0.5 fps je maximální úspora ale auto by mohlo mezi tiky projet.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "OCR fps during idle mode. 1 fps = 1 OCR cycle per second, big savings. Higher (2–5) reduces response time for cars entering without motion. 0.5 fps is the maximum saving but a car could pass between ticks."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Noční pauza detekce": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Night pause"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "V nastaveném časovém okně se úplně zastaví OCR / commit / webhook na obou kamerách. Stream + náhled běží dál (žádný reconnect). Použití: pokud se brána mechanicky uzavře (zámek, závora) a nemá smysl detekovat. Pokud začátek > konec, okno přechází přes půlnoc (např. 23 → 5 znamená 23:00–04:59).": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Within the configured time window, OCR / commit / webhook are paused on both cameras. Stream + preview keep running (no reconnect). Use case: when the gate is mechanically locked and detection is pointless. If start > end, the window crosses midnight (e.g. 23 → 5 means 23:00–04:59)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Filtr čtení SPZ": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Plate reading filter"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Jak velký musí být text v záběru kamery \\(cam.label), aby ho aplikace zkusila přečíst. Menší = čte i drobnější plate (ale víc omylů); větší = ignoruje malé texty (loga, cedule). 0,05 je rozumný základ.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "How large the text must be in camera \\(cam.label)'s frame for the app to try to read it. Smaller = reads tinier plates (but more errors); larger = ignores small texts (logos, signs). 0.05 is a reasonable baseline."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Jak dlouho čekat než stejné auto může být zaznamenáno znovu. Platí pro obě kamery. Auto stojící před závorou by jinak spustilo desítky záznamů. 15 s je typické.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "How long to wait before the same car can be recorded again. Applies to both cameras. Without it, a car standing at the gate would trigger dozens of records. 15 s is typical."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Rychlý režim čtení": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fast read mode"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Zapne Apple Vision .fast model místo .accurate. Výsledek: ~2× rychlejší detekce (~14 fps vs ~7 fps per kamera), ale o ~10–15 % nižší přesnost na šikmých/špinavých SPZ. Pro firemní vjezd s čistým výhledem v pohodě; pro kameru sledující ulici z dálky raději nech vypnuté. Apple Vision framework vnitřně serializuje všechny OCR požadavky — proto jediná cesta k vyššímu fps je rychlejší model.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Switches Apple Vision to the .fast model instead of .accurate. Result: ~2× faster detection (~14 fps vs ~7 fps per camera), but ~10–15 % lower accuracy on tilted/dirty plates. Fine for company entrances with a clean view; for a street-distance camera, leave off. Apple Vision serializes OCR requests internally — switching the model is the only way to higher fps."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Dvojité čtení (2× přesnější)": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Double read (2× more accurate)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pustí na každý frame DVA Vision requesty paralelně (revision3 + revision2). Starší revize 2 občas chytne co revision3 mine a naopak → voting přes obě zvýší přesnost o 2–4 % na okrajových případech (špinavé / šikmé plate). FPS se sníží (~50 %), ANE využití se zvýší (~2×). Funguje pouze v přesném režimu (rychlý režim musí být vypnutý).": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Runs TWO Vision requests in parallel per frame (revision3 + revision2). Revision 2 sometimes catches what revision3 misses and vice versa → voting across both improves accuracy by 2–4 % on edge cases (dirty / tilted plates). FPS drops (~50 %), ANE usage rises (~2×). Works only in accurate mode (fast mode must be off)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Rectangle pre-filter (méně falešných)": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Rectangle pre-filter (fewer false positives)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Před text OCR spustí VNDetectRectanglesRequest, pak propouští jen observations uvnitř plate-shape rectangles (aspect 2.5–7:1). Filtruje false positives z okolních nápisů (VCHOD, FASE) na noisy background. Účtujeme ~5 ms Vision call navíc per OCR frame.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Before text OCR, runs a VNDetectRectanglesRequest and passes only observations inside plate-shaped rectangles (aspect 2.5–7:1). Filters false positives from surrounding signage (ENTRY, etc.) on noisy backgrounds. Costs ~5 ms extra Vision call per OCR frame."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pro commits s confidence < 0.85 spustí on-device LLM (Apple Intelligence) co zkoriguje OCR chyby (B↔8, O↔0, I↔1 atd.). Inference běží na ANE, ~200–500 ms per low-confidence commit, 1 s timeout. Accept korekce jen když je v známých SPZ nebo projde CZ/SK format validátorem.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "For commits with confidence < 0.85, runs an on-device LLM (Apple Intelligence) to correct OCR errors (B↔8, O↔0, I↔1, etc.). Inference runs on ANE, ~200–500 ms per low-confidence commit, 1 s timeout. Corrections are accepted only if in the known plates list or if they pass the CZ/SK format validator."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Rozpoznání typu + barvy vozidla": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vehicle type + color recognition"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "K každému commitu přidá vehicle type (SUV/truck/van/bus/motorcycle/car) a dominantní barvu (black/white/red/blue/silver/gray atd.) extrahovanou z crop image. Apple Vision VNClassifyImage (Imagenet-1K) + CIAreaAverage color. ~10 ms per commit na ANE/GPU. Zobrazí se v RecentRow pod SPZ.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Adds vehicle type (SUV/truck/van/bus/motorcycle/car) and dominant color (black/white/red/blue/silver/gray, etc.) extracted from the crop image to every commit. Apple Vision VNClassifyImage (Imagenet-1K) + CIAreaAverage color. ~10 ms per commit on ANE/GPU. Shown in RecentRow below the plate."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Swin2SR ML upscaler 4× pro snapshot quality. Běží jen na GPU/CPU (CoreML EP s useCPUAndGPU=true) → žádná contention s Vision OCR na ANE. Cena ~80 ms/snapshot, 32 MB model. Master kill-switch pro celý SR layer (snapshot + OCR shadow + live OCR). Default ON.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Swin2SR ML upscaler 4× for snapshot quality. Runs only on GPU/CPU (CoreML EP with useCPUAndGPU=true) → no contention with Vision OCR on ANE. Cost ~80 ms/snapshot, 32 MB model. Master kill-switch for the whole SR layer (snapshot + OCR shadow + live OCR). Default ON."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Vývojářské logy (verbose trace)": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Developer logs (verbose trace)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Podrobný per-frame log do ~/Library/Application Support/SPZ/spz.log — preprocess luminance, Vision timing, obs count, normalizer raw/basic text, motion detection, vehicle color sample RGB atd. ~20 MB/hodinu log IO, VYPNOUT v produkci.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Detailed per-frame log to ~/Library/Application Support/SPZ/spz.log — preprocess luminance, Vision timing, observation count, normalizer raw/basic text, motion detection, vehicle color sample RGB, etc. ~20 MB/hour of log IO, TURN OFF in production."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Vylepšené čtení (pass 2)": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Enhanced reading (pass 2)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Použít enhanced retry jako hlavní čtečku": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Use enhanced retry as the primary reader"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pass 1 najde oblast textu, pass 2 přečte tight výřez s lokální úpravou jasu a kontrastu. Když enhanced čtení projde CZ/SK validací, dostane přednost v hlasování.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pass 1 finds the text area, pass 2 reads a tight crop with local brightness and contrast adjustment. If the enhanced reading passes CZ/SK validation, it takes priority in voting."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Vyšší práh pustí pass 2 i na sebevědomá, ale často chybná Vision čtení typu 0↔3, B↔8 nebo S↔5. 0,95 je konzervativní default pro M4.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A higher threshold runs pass 2 even on confident but often wrong Vision readings like 0↔3, B↔8 or S↔5. 0.95 is a conservative default for M4."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Váha enhanced hlasu": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Enhanced vote weight"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Kolikrát silnější je pass 2 hlas proti běžnému pass 1 hlasu. Nezahazuje raw čtení, jen posouvá rozhodování ke zřetelnějšímu cropu.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "How much stronger the pass 2 vote is vs. the regular pass 1 vote. Doesn't discard raw reads, just shifts the decision toward the clearer crop."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Váha raw hlasu při překryvu": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Raw vote weight on overlap"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Když pass 1 a pass 2 míří na stejnou oblast, raw hlas se zjemní. Bez překryvu zůstává raw hlas plný, aby se neztratil druhý objekt v záběru.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When pass 1 and pass 2 target the same area, the raw vote softens. Without overlap, the raw vote stays full so a second object in view isn't lost."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Maximum enhanced výřezů": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Maximum enhanced crops"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Kolik Y-clusterů textu může pass 2 znovu číst v jednom OCR ticku. 2 pokryje SPZ + okrajový druhý objekt bez zbytečného ANE tlaku.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "How many text Y-clusters pass 2 may re-read per OCR tick. 2 covers a plate + an edge second object without unnecessary ANE pressure."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sekundární OCR engine": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Secondary OCR engine"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Použít sekundární OCR plugin": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Use secondary OCR plugin"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Vypínatelný druhý OCR engine pro cross-validaci textu na výřezu SPZ. Běží přes ONNX Runtime, bez CoreML konverze. Když model není přibalený, chování detekce se nemění.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Toggleable second OCR engine for cross-validation of plate text. Runs via ONNX Runtime, no CoreML conversion. When the model isn't bundled, detection behavior is unchanged."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Váha cross-validovaného hlasu": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cross-validated vote weight"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Když se Apple Vision a sekundární engine shodnou, čtení dostane vyšší váhu v trackeru. 2,0 odpovídá zhruba dvěma nezávislým potvrzením v jednom frame.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When Apple Vision and the secondary engine agree, the reading gets a higher tracker weight. 2.0 roughly corresponds to two independent confirmations in one frame."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Typy značek": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Plate types"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Značky na přání (6–8 znaků)": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vanity plates (6–8 chars)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tzv. vanity SPZ — vlastní text zvolený majitelem (např. AHOJSVET). Pokud v provozu žádnou takovou značku nečekáš, nech vypnuté — jinak riskuješ, že aplikace chybně přečte reklamní text jako SPZ.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "So-called vanity plates — owner-chosen text (e.g. AHOJSVET). If you don't expect any in your traffic, leave off — otherwise the app may misread an advertising text as a plate."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Zahraniční značky (DE/AT/PL/IT/ES)": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Foreign plates (DE/AT/PL/IT/ES)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Německo, Rakousko, Polsko, Itálie, Španělsko. Typicky ve formátu s pomlčkou (např. B-AB 1234). Pokud potkáš zahraniční auta, nech zapnuté.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Germany, Austria, Poland, Italy, Spain. Typically with a hyphen (e.g. B-AB 1234). If you have foreign cars, leave on."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Použité technologie": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Technologies used"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Engine čtení": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Reading engine"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sekundární OCR": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Secondary OCR"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Záchrana": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Rescue"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "top 3 kandidáti z každého pohledu": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "top 3 candidates from each view"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "CZ formát — zaměňuje O↔0 dle pozice": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "CZ format — swaps O↔0 by position"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sledování": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tracking"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "překryv + hlasování + shoda textu": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "overlap + voting + text match"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "(log je prázdný nebo nedostupný)": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "(log is empty or unavailable)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Shelly — výjezd": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Shelly — exit"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Příkaz pro otevření závory (legacy)": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gate-open command (legacy)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pouze pro známé SPZ": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Only for known plates"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Když zapnuto, otevře závoru POUZE autům ze seznamu známých SPZ. Když vypnuto, otevře každému autu (včetně neznámých) — nedoporučeno pro ostrý provoz.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When enabled, opens the gate ONLY for cars on the known plates list. When disabled, opens for every car (including unknown) — not recommended for production."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Počet opakovaných pokusů": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Retry count"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pokud se nepodaří odeslat příkaz na závoru napoprvé (např. relé zrovna neodpovídá), kolikrát to zkusit znovu. 0 = zkusí jen jednou.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If the gate command fails on the first attempt (e.g. the relay doesn't respond), how many times to retry. 0 = single attempt."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "bez opakování": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "no retries"
